-10", "experiences/1/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:1081464", "experiences/1/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/1/jobDescription": "My job involved overseeing the day to day running of all restaurants in the La Monita group; two branches of La Monita,Santiaga, Billys Smokehouse and Michelin recommended Thai Niyom.\n\nI am also responsible for, amongst others;\n\nRecruitment and training across the group\nCreating and maintaining company policies and SOP's\nWorking alongside the culinary team on menu development & updates\nDeveloping marketing and promotional activities and liaising with the media \nCreating and achieving financial budgets and delivering financial report to the owners\nEnsuring company wide health and safety compliance\nEnsuring guest satisfaction, complaint handling and trouble shooting", "experiences/1/jobEndedOn": "12-2024", "experiences/1/jobLocation": "Bangkok, Bangkok City, Thailand", "experiences/1/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/1/jobStartedOn": "3-2024", "experiences/1/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/1/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C4E0BAQHONNR1vEby9A/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1631335505266?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=CElVjBm-oYuyU4nCw6P9Y0oN1vqcFTEOXEpkrgpRvBA", "experiences/1/title": "Group General Manager", "experiences/2/companyId": "80806716", "experiences/2/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/peppina-asia/", "experiences/2/companyName": "Peppina Asia", "experiences/2/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:80806716", "experiences/2/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "I held the position of COO  for Peppina, an Italian pizzeria concept and hospitality management company in Thailand, which garnered numerous accolades under my leadership.\nIn 2023, we ranked 19th globally in the 50 Top Artisan Pizza Chain awards and earned the prestigious \"Il Fritturista\" award for our Neapolitan fried snacks. Earlier, in 2022, we were honored as Thailand's best pizzer